Class ServeEvent

java.lang.Object

ServeEvent
public class ServeEvent extends Event
The ServeEvent class extends the Event class and provides for the implementation of the Customer serving process.

    • nextEvent

      public Pair<Event,ImList<Server>> nextEvent(ImList<Server> inputList)
      ServeEvent's implementation of the nextEvent method. The ending time of service is determined by invoking the customer's supplied service duration time. The ending time is then used to generate a DoneEvent which is returned together with the updated availability of the server.
